Description:
Extra details of an item that will show when a user queries something in the terminal.
{0} is the item ID, example: HSU_123.
{1} is the item status: Normal, Malfunctioning, Deactivated, Powered, or UnPowered.
{2} is the zone it's in.
{3} is either InGame.Terminal.Ping_out_of_range_X or InGame.Terminal.In_range_for_ping_X
name: InGame.Terminal.DefaultItemDetails
